Class position

java.lang.Object
javafx.scene.Node
javafx.scene.shape.Shape
javafx.scene.shape.Rectangle
position
All Implemented Interfaces:
javafx.css.Styleable, javafx.event.EventTarget
public class position
extends javafx.scene.shape.Rectangle
Position Provides logic for each individual grid position on our boards. Each grid position is a rectangle, so we extend rectangle class

    • isGuess

      public boolean isGuess()
      Method to return if position on grid has been guessed or not guessed.
      Returns:
      boolean. If position is already guessed return true, if not return false

    • getOccupied

      public boolean getOccupied()
      Method to return if position on grid is occupied by a game piece.
      Returns:
      boolean. Return true if piece of ship is located on grid position, return false if empty.
